    section.product--superscribe#superscribe
      .content
        img.product-icon src="/images/superscribe-icon.png" alt="Superscribe icon" width="64"
        h2.product-title Superscribe
        p.product-summary Distraction-free comic script editor for Mac and Windows.
        p Don't worry about numbering pages and panels. Forget about switching
          between headings, action, characters and dialog. Let
          Superscribe handle the formatting and page/panel numbering as you type.
          Fewer distractions means faster writing and easier editing.
        p The superscript syntax was inspired by markdown and fountain. One hashtag creates a page heading.
          Two hashtags create a panel heading. Superscribe inserts the page and
          panel numbers automatically, as you type.
        ul
          li Automatic page, panel and dialog numbering
          li Contextual formatting as you type
          li Displays your dialog word count; per speech bubble, per panel and per page
          li Page breaks before each page heading
          li Spell check
          li Print or export to PDF
        p.product-links
          a.product-link href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/superscribe/id1193005924?mt=12" event-category="Superscribe" event-action="click" event-label="App Store"
